---
---
<section style="border-top: 1px solid #1e1e35;">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-10 font-mono" style="color: #e2e8f0;">
      <span style="color: #6366f1;">#</span> How it works
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-3 tabular-nums" style="color: #6366f1;">01</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-2" style="color: #e2e8f0;">Install &amp; configure</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8b95a1;">
          Run the single Go binary via Docker, Homebrew, or APT. Configure with
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: #161625; color: #cbd5e0; border: 1px solid #1e1e35;">FUNNELBARN_*</span>
          env vars — API key, admin credentials, DB path, CORS origins.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-3 tabular-nums" style="color: #6366f1;">02</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-2" style="color: #e2e8f0;">Add the SDK</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8b95a1;">
          Drop in the JavaScript snippet for automatic page view tracking, or use the Node.js or Python SDK for server-side events.
          One-line setup, async flush so it never blocks your app.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-3 tabular-nums" style="color: #6366f1;">03</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-2" style="color: #e2e8f0;">Analyze</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8b95a1;">
          Open the dashboard for time-series charts, top pages, referrers, and UTM attribution. Define funnels, run A/B tests, and watch the live event feed — all on your infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
